      • validate

        void validate(T propValue,
              String path,
              String name)
        Validate a property value. Throws ValidateException If validation failed.
        Parameters:
        propValue - The property value.
        path - The path of the JSON document. e.g. "Group.Users[0].Address".
        name - The property name of the JSON document. e.g. "zipcode".
